text: Cornatzer is an unincorporated community in Davie County, North Carolina. It is located at the intersection Cornatzer Road (SR 1606/SR 1616) and Milling Road (SR 1600). It is named after the Cornatzer family that resided in then Advance, NC and sold their farm to R.J. Reynolds Tobacco Company. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Davie County, North Carolina Category:Unincorporated communities in North Carolina
